---
metadata:
  name: Content card
  params:
    variant:
      - default
      - featured
      - small
    content: This is an example card
    imgSrc: ''
    tags: []
  styleguide:
    - variant: featured
      content: This is an example card
      imgSrc: 'https://picsum.photos/495/290?random=1'
      tags:
        - tag
        - longertag
        - longertag
        - longertag
    - variant: default
      content: This is an example card
      imgSrc: 'https://picsum.photos/317/192?random=2'

---
{% liquid
  assign variant = params.variant | default: 'default'
  assign content = params.content
  assign imgSrc = params.imgSrc
  assign tags = params.tags | parse_json | default: '[]' | parse_json

  assign button_params = null | hash_merge: weight: 'primary', content: 'Read more'

%}
<div class="flex">
  <div><img src="{{imgSrc}}"></div>
  <div class="p-6" style="max-width: 460px;">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-interactive-text">Blog post title lorem ispum dolor sit amet</h2>
    <div class="flex">
      {% for tag in tags %}
      <div class="mr-2 cursor-pointer">
        {% assign chip_params = '{}' | parse_json | hash_merge: closable: false, variant: 'clickable', content: tag %}
        {% theme_render_rc 'components/molecules/chip', params: chip_params %}
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div>
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aliquam eget auctor nunc. Nam nec lacus quis lectus egestas ultricies. Phasellus molestie gravida justo in fringilla. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
    </div>
    <div class="flex">
      {% theme_render_rc 'components/atoms/button', params: button_params %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
